The ICU costs 20,000 yuan a day, and the elderly stay there for four years.
Netizens are hotly discussing "Where did my medical insurance go?"

20,000*365*4=29,200,000
Last year, the basic medical insurance fund for urban and rural residents spent 927.3 billion yuan, the number of insured people was 983.49 million, and the average expenditure per person was 942 yuan.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Some Chinese people are really psychologically twisted. They only care about "comparison" and not their actual situation.
No matter how hard, difficult or serious the situation is, as long as they hear that other people in other places are worse off than themselves, they can find honey in the suffering.
But they overlooked one thing. Even if the entire American continent disappeared from the earth, the exploitation and suffering you have to face will not be reduced at all.
